'''Lvl-3 Enchant''' is a [[utility spell]] in the [[standard spellbook]], requiring level 49 [[Magic]] to cast. The spell enchants [[ruby]] and [[red topaz]] items, primarily [[jewellery]], granting 59 Magic experience when doing so.

This spell can be transferred to a [[Enchant ruby or topaz|magic tablet]] by bringing the required runes and a piece of [[soft clay]] to a [[lectern]] in the [[study]] of a [[player-owned house]], granting the same experience as casting the spell.

